{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, AI supports digital farming that aims to limit carbon footprint and contribute toward environmental sustainability.",
    "Similarly, incorporation of AI into agriculture sector could gain higher economic gains (Ryan et al., 2023).",
    "It has been reported that a higher tendency of firms adopting AI was witnessed during the last decade (Davenport et al., 2020).",
    "Consequently, envisaging the agriculture sector with AI technologies would create novel economic opportunities locally and globally.",
    "Additionally, Agricultural AI concentrating on external elements employs data related to crop values, market patterns, consumer preferences, needs, and visual aspects (Dharmaraj and Vijayanand, 2018)."
  ]
}